**Dragon's Tale** is a MMO casino operated by Andrew Tepper.

The game is a free download.

A [review of the service](http://bensonsamuel.wordpress.com/2012/09/26/dragons-tale-play-to-win-bitcoin/) describes some details.

On February 6, 2011 the beta release of the game was celebrated with a Grand Opening Party in which over 1,000 bitcoins were awarded (1.1)

